description: Record to support submission of GeneRIFs for a gene not in Gene (Agrobacterium genomic group 9; Agrobacterium genomic species 9; Agrobacterium genomic species G9; Agrobacterium genomosp. 9; Agrobacterium tumefaciens genomovar G9.  Use when strain, subtype, isolate, etc. is unspecified, or when different from all specified ones in Gene.).
